@s1monw Actually I've found two bugs in the `query_string` query from the above.  More clearly demonstrated here:

```
curl -XPUT "http://localhost:9200/test/product/1" -d'
{
   "desc": "one two three"
}'

curl -XPUT "http://localhost:9200/test/customer/2" -d'
